An official federal updated information on the SBV findings in Germany, including a map, would be gratefully welcomed. - Mod.AS]

On 24 Jan 2012, the CVO (chief veterinarian officer) of the United Kingdom submitted to the OIE an official notification on the occurrence of an emerging disease caused by the Schmallenberg virus; see, with map, at http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=11539. - Mod.AS.]
